              li.skill-item: a(href="") PostgreSQL
              li.skill-item: a(href="") Adobe Photoshop
              li.skill-item: a(href="") Heroku
    #projects.content-area.light
      .content
        .container
          .row
            .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
              h2.text-center Recent Work
              .project-items
                .row.project-item
                  .project-image.col-sm-6
                    img(src="./img/nycda-main.png")
                  .project-content.col-sm-6
                    h3: a(href="http://nycda.com" target="_blank") NYCDA Home
                    p New York Code + Design Academy was in need of a web overhaul. I am currently lead developer and have planned, designed, and developed this project. It's purpose is to allow students to request information, apply, pay-for, and enroll into any of the courses offered at NYCDA. The entire process is automated and tracked for easier analytic collection.
                    p.toolbox Ruby on Rails · Sass · JavaScript/jQuery · PostgreSQL · Haml · Git + Github · Stripe · Heroku

                .row.project-item
                  .project-image.col-sm-6
                    img(src="./img/nycda-ams.png")
                  .project-content.col-sm-6
                    h3: a(href="http://nycda.com/study-in-amsterdam" target="_blank") NYCDA Amsterdam
                    p New York Code + Design Academy launched a Web Development class in Amsterdam and I was asked to create a landing-page for this course. I developed this lander from scratch using nothing but an oversized spoon and some string.
                    p.toolbox Jade · Sass · JavaScript/jQuery · Git + Github · Flexbox
                    
                .row.project-item
                  .project-image.col-sm-6
                    img(src="./img/itsraider.png")
                  .project-content.col-sm-6
                    h3: a(href="http://itsraider.com" target="_blank") Raider
                    p Raider is my musical alias (not so much of an alias I suppose). I created this website to showcase my music as well as to offer a way to contact me. It was developed from the ground up using CSS-grid-framework, Skeleton.
                    p.toolbox Jade · Sass · Responsive Design · Git + Github
                    
    #contact.content-area.dark
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
            h2.text-center Drop me a line...
            form(action="//formspree.io/adamjraider@gmail.com" method="POST")
              .field
                label(for="name") Your name, please?
                input(name="name" type="text", required)
              .field
                label(for="email") Email address?
                input(name="_replyto" type="text" required)
              .field
                label(for="message") What's up?
                textarea(name="message" rows="4" required)
              .hidden
                input(type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Hey Adam! (A message from http://adamraider.me)")
                input(type="text" name="_gotcha" style="display:none")
              .field.text-center
                input.button(type="submit" value="Let's chat!" title="Let's chat!")
    #footer.aside-area.light
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
            .text-center
              h4 Adam Raider
              ul.nav-social
                li: a(href="http://github.com/adamraider" target="_blank"): i.fa.fa-github-square
                li: a(href="http://twitter.com/ixraider" target="_blank"): i.fa.fa-twitter-square
                li: a(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adamjraider" target="_blank"): i.fa.fa-linkedin-square
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            .text-right
              p.muted &copy; 2016
